paragraphs.title: Inner join on tool and time
paragraphs.text:
%spark2.spark

val matchedDF = sensorDF.join(faultDF, sensorDF("Tool") === faultDF("Tool") && sensorDF("time") === faultDF("time") , joinType="inner").drop(faultDF("Tool")).drop(faultDF("time"))

matchedDF.registerTempTable("matchedDF")
